Compare LightGBM vs Random Model¶

In [93]:
class RandomModelTest:
    def __init__(self, order_flow_len):
        self.order_flow_len = order_flow_len
    
    def create_order_flow(self):
        return np.random.choice([-1,0,1],p=[0.05,0.9,0.05], size = self.order_flow_len)
    
    def create_pnl_data(self):
        balance = bt.Balance(100)
        current_price = pred_test.price.values
        prediction_price_ahead = np.random.normal(np.mean(pred_test.price.pct_change()),
                                                  np.std(pred_test.price.pct_change()),
                                                  size = len(pred_test.price.values)
                                                 )
        # prediction_price_ahead = []
        rule_based_trade_order = bt.RuleBasedOrderExecution.higher_lower_flow_interval
        rule_based_amount_alloc = bt.RuleBasedAmountAllocation.allocate_const(1)
        min_trade_interval = 13  #minimum trade price tick interval for order, every 13 ticks the order will be alocated
        pred_trade_interval = 13 # prediction_price_ahead_train interval ticks ahead
        bid_ask_spread = 0
        commision = 0
        back_testRandomModel = bt.BackTest(balance,
                                           current_price,
                                           prediction_price_ahead,
                                           rule_based_trade_order,
                                           rule_based_amount_alloc,
                                           min_trade_interval,
                                           pred_trade_interval,
                                           bid_ask_spread,
                                           commision,
                                           upper_q,
                                           lower_q)
        # order_flow = self.create_order_flow()
        order_flow = back_testRandomModel.create_order_flow()
        back_testRandomModel.calc_balance(order_flow)
        return order_flow, balance.pnl_history, balance.balance_history
